{"tid":980722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑜珈妹穿高衩緊身衣「邪惡視角露蜜桃臀」　網狂喊：OMG","createTime":"2019-01-13T17:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T03:32:19.000Z","uid":212399,"like":40,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c538b14cf62d05ecb05fc2a99271eea865340405","tid":980722,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3830/d3830926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3830%2Fd3830926.jpg&h=51be29b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 首爾瑜珈正妹近日再度登上PTT表特版。（圖／翻攝自IG／Sanga_yogini）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n南韓首爾一名瑜珈正妹近日再度登上PTT表特版，可見她擺出許多高難度的姿勢，倒立、劈腿也難不倒她，加上天使臉孔和魔鬼身材的組合，讓網友紛紛直呼「那個曲線OMG」、「這些姿勢太讚了！」<br />\nPTT網友11日以標題「YOGA的多種姿勢II」PO出多張照片，穿著白色緊身衣的她做出身體貼地、單腳高舉空中的姿勢，露出白嫩蜜大腿和蜜桃臀。根據她的IG和Youtube頻道，她時常分享練瑜珈的影片和美照。<br />\n許多網友看了留言提到，「身材太吸睛，不知道花多少時間在運動」、「看完覺得我自己的身體好硬，也想練一下瑜珈」、「有大膽的想法」、「這身材真是讚到不行啊」。<br />\n▼影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VDVql85qSQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVDVql85qSQQ&d=omOpuDpu%2BCskMQmwPHXVB4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e6b6852f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VDVql85qSQQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I_UZtbwHw34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI_UZtbwHw34&d=omOpuDpu%2BCskMQmwPHXVB4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b442ff83\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I_UZtbwHw34</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cBYJ3S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cBYJ3S.jpg&h=4a78f21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fW4SOvy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfW4SOvy.jpg&h=fc3c9bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31s86hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31s86hd.jpg&h=4f6c67c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewayxXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewayxXe.jpg&h=18c0eb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190113/1355214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190113%2F1355214.htm&d=omOpuDpu%2BCskMQmwPHXVB4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c61d9009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190113/1355214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"42dbfb26f94546567bfe55174e4073c05f879661","tid":980722,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5692ef140d7a63e31db767bbd9bd5b2f06158b39","tid":980722,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:24:57.000Z","msg":"高潮腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1729389b14c32f55fb0051c903d9f286703e4bf0","tid":980722,"uid":89514,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T21:10:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48aa048d75f16bcec46b5f6d708f1f17843f3ec8","tid":980722,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T22:40:50.000Z","msg":"上ig打j cap幾張圖post上ptt都上到台灣新聞"},{"pid":"9c44ac2938f0710750b62629c9a1635a8a2a90d3","tid":980722,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1729389b14c32f55fb0051c903d9f286703e4bf0","tid":980722,"uid":89514,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T21:10:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T23:24:17.000Z","msg":"冇計，年紀大，發現身材都好重要"},{"pid":"3e42fcd3820c04e9def0340980e5a131cace27c4","tid":980722,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T23:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af43a2